**Why This Is Dangerous**:
- Full probability distributions allow attackers to use gradient-based optimization to reconstruct training samples
- No rate limiting enables thousands of queries needed for model inversion
- Exact confidence scores leak information about training data distribution
- No query monitoring means attacks go undetected

**SECURE VERSION**:

